        "----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        "<center>\n",
        "<font size = '6' color =violet><u><b>WHERE<b/></u></font>\n",
        "</center>\n",
        "\n",
        "Si tuviéramos una tabla con cien millones de filas de datos, leer todas las filas sería ineficiente y quizás incluso imposible.\n",
        "\n",
        "Para filtrar ciertos resultados, debemos usar una **WHERE** cláusula en la consulta. Esta cláusula se aplica a cada fila de datos, verificando valores de columnas específicas para determinar si debe incluirse en los resultados o no.\n",
        "\n",
        "![3.png](data:image/png;base64,)\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "T7ES0wi7UxNe"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Se pueden construir cláusulas más complejas combinando palabras clave numerosas AND ó OR lógicas (por ejemplo, num_wheels >= 4 AND doors <= 2). A continuación, se muestran algunos operadores útiles que puede utilizar para datos numéricos (por ejemplo, enteros o de punto flotante):\n",
        "\n",
        "![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "![5.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "tYXbQCFwWdRC"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "La condición puede usar:\n",
        "\n",
        "* Comparaciones (=, <>, >, <, >=, <=).\n",
        "* Operadores lógicos (AND, OR, NOT).\n",
        "* Funciones (BETWEEN, IN, LIKE, IS NULL, etc.)."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "RJPfXzgOXZf8"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "<font size = '4' color =violet><u><b>Ejemplo básico de WHERE:<b/></u></font>\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        "SELECT *\n",
        "\n",
        "FROM empleados\n",
        "\n",
        "WHERE departamento = 'Ventas';\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        " * Devuelve solo los empleados del departamento de Ventas\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Zi_JC2QwmFq5"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "<font size = '4' color =violet><u><b>WHERE con operadores de comparación:<b/></u></font>\n",
        "\n",
        "* <u>Mayor que</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM productos WHERE precio > 100;\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* <u>Diferente de</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM empleados WHERE cargo != 'Gerente';\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* <u>Menor o igual</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM pedidos WHERE cantidad <= 50;\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hKMf4Mvsm_YT"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "<font size = '4' color =violet><u><b>WHERE con operadores lógicos:<b/></u></font>\n",
        "\n",
        "* <u>Dos condiciones (AND)</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM clientes\n",
        "WHERE pais = 'España' AND ciudad = 'Madrid';\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "* <u>Una u otra (OR)</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM clientes\n",
        "WHERE ciudad = 'Madrid' OR ciudad = 'Barcelona';\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        " * <u>Negación (NOT)</u>\n",
        "\n",
        "SELECT * FROM productos\n",
        "WHERE NOT categoria = 'Electrónica';\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "DubPSOBDn0MC"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "skKTseKhX2x8"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "<font size = '4' color =violet><u><b>Sintaxis general<b/></u></font>\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        "SELECT *\n",
        "\n",
        "FROM pedidos\n",
        "\n",
        "WHERE estado IN ('Pendiente','Enviado');\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        " * Equivalente a varias condiciones OR.\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Eo6MqAP4X3Hl"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "\n",
        "<font size = '4' color =violet><u><b>Ejemplo combinado con múltiples condiciones:<b/></u></font>\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        "SELECT *\n",
        "\n",
        "FROM empleados\n",
        "\n",
        "WHERE (departamento = 'Ventas' OR departamento = 'Marketing')\n",
        "\n",
        "  ---AND salario > 2000\n",
        "\n",
        "  ---AND fecha_contratacion >= '2024-01-01';\n",
        "\n",
        "-----------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
        " *  Devuelve empleados de Ventas o Marketing, con salario > 2000 y contratados desde 2024.\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hcn-utE3YSXC"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "<font size = '5' color =violet><u><b>Errores comunes con WHERE:<b/></u></font>"
      ],
